-- MOVES-Citi Global Markets hires top investment banker in Germany 
-- 
-- Wed Oct 01, 2014 01:15PM EDT
-- None



Oct 1 (Reuters) - Citigroup Global Markets Deutschland AG [CRPHDG.UL] has appointed Sven Baumann to its investment banking business.

Baumann will join the company in London at the beginning of 2015, before moving to Frankfurt as managing director. He will work for private equity clients as well as some selected corporate clients at Citi.